---
title: Smart Barramundi and Horseradish Remoulade with Warm Potato and Snap Pea Salad
description: Not your regular potato salad – this smart version packs in sweet snap peas, pickles and smoked paprika for a burst of colour and layers of flavour! To top it all off, juicy barramundi fillets get a generous dollop of punchy remoulade.

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amount.
